ENTRY            F0642   20251217   20260305   20260305       F105
SUBENT        F0642001   20251217   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                 10         21
TITLE      Elastic alpha + 28Si scattering - thick target
           measurements and results
AUTHOR     (P.Manngard)
INSTITUTE  (2SF ABA)
REFERENCE  (J,ZP/A,349,335,1994)
FACILITY   (VDGT,2SWDUPP) The Svedberg tandem accelerator in
           Uppsala, Sweden (Ea=6.5-12.7 MeV) with the energy
           step 300 keV down to E = 8.8 MeV and 200 keV for the
           lower energies.
           (ISOCY,2SF ABA) The thick target measurements were
           carried out at the Abo Akademi Accelerator Laboratory
            (E = 12.5 - 19 MeV) with the energy step 400 keV.
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) The setup consisted of 7 Si surface barrier
           detectors spaced 10 degr. apart, which then were
           rotated twice by 3 degr.
ADD-RES    (COMP) The result is compared to an old GCM phase shift
           prediction taken from literature.
SAMPLE     The thick target of 28Si.
METHOD     (TTM)
HISTORY    (20040528C)
           (20251217U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              21
COMMON               3          3
ANG        EN-ERR-DIG ERR-DIG
ADEG       MEV        MB/SR
       173.      0.010        1.6
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           28
SUBENT        F0642002   20251217   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                  3          3
REACTION   (14-SI-28(A,EL)14-SI-28,,DA)
STATUS     (CURVE,,P.Manngard,J,ZP/A,349,335,1994) Fig.2
HISTORY    (20251217U) SD: BIB updated.
ENDBIB               3
